short_description.html: Sometimes inspiration comes in the form of the song, like these adidas x Bad Bunny Adizero SL72 Shoes, which draw on Benito's own "Telefono Nuevo". These shoes bring in a remix, combining SL72 upper with an Adizero bottom to create an entirely new look that celebrates our archives. The result is a mash up of materials and colours — all a tribute to the original materials and colours that the different shoes first launched with. "PARA BAD BUNNY" signs off the 3-Stripes.
